                    "maskingDescription": "Participants and care providers will not be told of their group allocation. Participants in the sham group will receive a brief stimulation of the scalp, which will give them a feeling of being stimulated. This sham stimulation has been shown to effectively blind participants to group. Assessors will not be told the type of study being conducted.",
